---

<main class="kawaii-shell page-shell" data-home-shell data-active={initialActive}>
  <header class="topbar">
    <button class="theme-toggle" type="button" data-theme-toggle aria-label="切换深色模式" aria-pressed="false">
      <svg class="moon-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M19.5 14.5A8.5 8.5 0 0 1 9.5 4.5a8.5 8.5 0 1 0 10 10Z" />
      </svg>
    </button>

    <nav class="topnav" aria-label="页面切换">
      <span class="topnav-indicator" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      {tabs.map((tab) => (
        <a
          href={tab.href}
          data-tab-target={tab.key}
          aria-current={tab.key === initialActive ? "page" : undefined}
        >
          {tab.label}
        </a>
      ))}
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="card-stage" aria-live="polite">
    <div class="card-viewport">
      <div class="card-track">
        <div class="card-panel">
          <article class="sample-card" data-card-panel="about">
            <div class="sample-inner">
              <section class="sample-hero">
                <p class="sample-kicker">Profile Surface / 关于奈月</p>
                <h1 class="sample-title">关于奈月</h1>
                <p class="sample-copy">
                  这是个人主页的内容卡片 demo，用来测试真实内容替换前的排版边界：
                  中日英混排、长句、短标签、列表、表格、代码片段、不同高度区块和页面滚动。
                </p>

                <div class="sample-card-accent" aria-label="标签示例">
                  <span class="sample-chip">中文简体</span>
                  <span class="sample-chip" lang="ja">日本語</span>
                  <span class="sample-chip">English</span>
                  <span class="sample-chip">2026.06</span>
                  <span class="sample-chip">soft mica</span>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-stats" aria-label="基础信息示例">
                  {heroStats.map(([label, value]) => (
                    <div class="hero-stat">
                      <span>{label}</span>
                      <strong>{value}</strong>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <h2>小卡片排版</h2>
                  <p>测试等宽网格、短标题、长说明和多语言内容。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="demo-grid demo-grid--four">
                  {profileCards.map((item) => (
                    <section class="demo-block">
                      <h3>{item.title}</h3>
                      <p lang={item.lang}>{item.text}</p>
                    </section>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section demo-section--split">
                <blockquote class="demo-quote">
                  “这里不是博客列表，而是一个干净的入口页面。内容可以很轻，但边界测试必须足够重。”
                </blockquote>

                <div class="demo-panel">
                  <h2>阅读节奏</h2>
                  <p>
                    这个面板测试较长段落。真实内容可能会介绍名字、角色气质、展示入口和一些偏好。
                    即使段落变长，卡片也应该只自然增长，不产生横向滚动。
                  </p>
                  <ul class="demo-list">
                    {rhythmItems.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <h2>多语言与长文本</h2>
                  <p>验证 Noto 字体系、长 token 和不同语言在同一区域的表现。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="demo-table" aria-label="字体和换行测试">
                  {typographyChecks.map((item) => (
                    <div>
                      <span>{item.label}</span>
                      <strong lang={item.lang}>{item.value}</strong>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section demo-section--split">
                <div class="demo-code" aria-label="代码片段示例">
                  <div class="demo-code-head">
                    <span>demo.config.ts</span>
                    <button type="button" data-copy-button>复制</button>
                  </div>
                  <pre><code>{`export const profile = {
  name: "奈月",
  theme: ["moon", "cat", "violet"],
  updated: "2026-06-17",
};`}</code></pre>
                </div>

                <div class="demo-notices">
                  {calloutItems.map((item) => <p>{item}</p>)}
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <h2>链接与按钮测试</h2>
                  <p>这些仍然是 demo。正式内容迁移时，只需要替换数据和文案，不需要依赖固定长度。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="link-list" aria-label="普通超链接示例">
                  {inlineLinks.map((item) => (
                    <p>
                      <strong>{item.label}</strong>
                      <a href={item.href} target={item.href.startsWith("http") ? "_blank" : undefined} rel={item.href.startsWith("http") ? "noreferrer" : undefined}>
                        {item.text}
                      </a>
                    </p>
                  ))}
                </div>

                <div class="action-demo" data-action-demo>
                  <div class="action-row">
                    {actionDemos.map((item) => (
                      <button
                        class:list={["demo-button", item.tone === "primary" && "demo-button--primary"]}
                        type="button"
                        data-demo-action={item.result}
                        disabled={item.disabled}
                      >
                        {item.label}
                      </button>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                  <p data-demo-action-output>按钮状态：尚未触发。</p>
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <h2>时间线与键值表</h2>
                  <p>这里故意让内容更长，用来测试宽屏下的页面滚动和顶栏沉浸状态。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="demo-timeline" aria-label="时间线示例">
                  {timelineItems.map((item) => (
                    <section class="demo-timeline-item">
                      <time>{item.time}</time>
                      <div>
                        <h3>{item.title}</h3>
                        <p>{item.text}</p>
                      </div>
                    </section>
                  ))}
                </div>

                <dl class="sample-meta">
                  {detailRows.map(([label, value]) => (
                    <div>
                      <dt>{label}</dt>
                      <dd>{value}</dd>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </dl>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <h2>更长内容块</h2>
                  <p>让关于页明显长于联系页，便于检查不同高度面板切换和滚动位置重置。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="demo-grid">
                  {featureNotes.map((item) => (
                    <section class="demo-block demo-block--wide">
                      <h3>{item.title}</h3>
                      <p>{item.text}</p>
                    </section>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="card-panel">
          <article class="sample-card" data-card-panel="find">
            <div class="sample-inner">
              <section class="sample-hero">
                <p class="sample-kicker">Contact Surface / 找到奈月</p>
                <h1 class="sample-title">找到奈月</h1>
                <p class="sample-copy">
                  这里是社交媒体和联系方式聚合页 demo。它测试外链、邮箱、待补充状态、长链接、状态标签、
                  可点击卡片和不可点击卡片的视觉差异。
                </p>

                <div class="demo-toolbar" aria-label="状态示例">
                  <span class="demo-status">可用</span>
                  <span class="demo-status demo-status--idle">待补充</span>
                  <span class="demo-status demo-status--soft">低频回复</span>
                  <span class="demo-status">外链</span>
                  <span class="demo-status demo-status--idle">邮箱</span>
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="demo-section">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <h2>入口卡片</h2>
                  <p>测试链接、不可点击状态、长 meta 文本和 hover 反馈。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-grid">
                  {contactLinks.map((item) =>
                    item.href ? (
                      <a
                        class="contact-card"
                        href={item.href}
                        target={item.href.startsWith("http") ? "_blank" : undefined}
                        rel={item.href.startsWith("http") ? "noreferrer" : undefined}
                      >
                        <div class="contact-card-head">
                          <h3>{item.label}</h3>
                          <span class="contact-pill">{item.tag}</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>{item.note}</p>
                        <span class="contact-meta">{item.meta}</span>
                      </a>
                    ) : (
                      <div class="contact-card contact-card--pending">
                        <div class="contact-card-head">
                          <h3>{item.label}</h3>
                          <span class="contact-pill contact-pill--muted">{item.tag}</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>{item.note}</p>
                        <span class="contact-meta">{item.meta}</span>
                      </div>
                    ),
                  )}
